这样写会更贴近你的实际贡献，不是“验证文档步骤”，而是将复杂故障场景自动化编排，并支持组合测试发现缺陷：
写作
Developed and enhanced the test framework based on AWS Power Outage recovery scenarios, enabling coordinated execution of multiple failure simulations through pipelines, including ASG configuration changes, EBS failures, and cross-component failover events. The framework supports different fault combinations to better replicate real-world outage conditions and has helped identify multiple defects and resilience gaps.
更适合年终总结（突出价值）：
写作
Designed and implemented framework enhancements to orchestrate complex AWS outage recovery experiments through automated pipelines. The solution enables simultaneous execution of infrastructure and application failure scenarios, supports flexible fault-injection combinations, and has contributed to the discovery of multiple defects, improving overall system resilience and recovery readiness.
如果是汇报时口语一点的说法：
写作
I enhanced our framework to automate AWS outage recovery experiments. Instead of running individual failure scenarios manually, the framework can trigger multiple events simultaneously, such as ASG changes, EBS failures, and component failovers, through pipelines. This allows us to test different fault combinations, better simulate real production incidents, and uncover defects that would be difficult to identify in isolated tests.
我觉得年终总结里第二个版本最合适，因为它突出了：
Framework设计与开发
自动化Pipeline编排
多故障同时注入
故障组合测试
发现多个缺陷
提升系统韧性（resilience）和恢复能力（recovery readiness）